I've grouped with many many Paladins in my time.  And the best ones don't have to be main tank to prove their worth.  They back up heal as needed.   They throw in some stuns here and there to keep casters from casting, particularly gate.  They do some crowd control if needed.  They help pull mobs off casters when a caster makes an oops.  They can root runners.  They can successfully tank unmezzable, unrootable adds.  They are effectively able to do a little of just about everything, and do it pretty darn well, if the player is skilled.  And for experience groups they do make a respectable main tank.<br>
